1\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute size-4 scale-0 rotate-90 transition-all dark:scale-100 dark:rotate-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl flex-1 px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><main class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-4 hidden justify-center lg:flex\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"leaderboard\"></div></div><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"CollectionPage\",\"name\":\"Free Media Toolkit\",\"description\":\"A collection of free browser-based tools for merging, converting, compressing, and trimming audio and video files.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/media-toolkit\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Media Toolkit\"}]}</script><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-4\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Media Toolkit</span></li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Free Media Toolkit</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-lg text-muted-foreground\">Merge, convert, compress, and trim audio and video files — a free alternative to Adobe Media Encoder. Everything runs in your browser.</p><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Nicolaus\",\"jobTitle\":\"Builder & Maintainer, Free Tool Shed\",\"description\":\"James Nicolaus builds and maintains every tool on Free Tool Shed. Each tool is designed, tested in real browsers across desktop and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\",\"worksFor\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\"}}</script><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Built and maintained by<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\" rel=\"author\" href=\"/about\">James Nicolaus</a></p><section aria-label=\"Summary\" class=\"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\">Free Tool Shed&#x27;s Media Toolkit is a browser-based suite for audio and video work: merge audiobook chapters, convert formats, compress video, trim clips, extract audio, pull subtitle tracks, and edit metadata. All processing runs locally via ffmpeg.wasm — no upload, no sign-up, no file-size cap beyond your machine&#x27;s memory. A free alternative to Adobe Media Encoder, HandBrake Online, and CloudConvert.</p></section><div class=\"mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><a href=\"/tools/media-toolkit/audio-merger\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"defau