<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-film size-4 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 3v18\"></path><path d=\"M3 7.5h4\"></path><path d=\"M3 12h18\"></path><path d=\"M3 16.5h4\"></path><path d=\"M17 3v18\"></path><path d=\"M17 7.5h4\"></path><path d=\"M17 16.5h4\"></path></svg><div data-slot=\"card-title\" class=\"font-heading font-medium group-data-[size=sm]/card:text-sm text-base\">Video Converter</div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-description\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Convert between MP4, WebM, MOV, AVI, and GIF. No uploads, no file size limits.</div></div></div></a><a href=\"/tools/media-toolkit/audio-trimmer\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card py-4 text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl relative h-full transition-colors hover:border-brand/50 hover:bg-muted/50\"><div data-slot=\"card-header\" class=\"group/card-header @container/card-header grid auto-rows-min items-start gap-1 rounded-t-xl px-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] has-data-[slot=card-description]:grid-rows-[auto_auto] [.border-b]:pb-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:[.border-b]:pb-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-scissors size-4 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M8.12 8.12 12 12\"></path><path d=\"M20 4 8.12 15.88\"></path><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M14.8 14.8 20 20\"></path></svg><div data-slot=\"card-title\" class=\"font-heading font-medium group-data-[size=sm]/card:text-sm text-base\">Audio Trimmer</div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-description\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Trim audio files or split them by time markers. Quick and precise cuts.</div></div></div></a><a href=\"/tools/media-toolkit/image-converter\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card py-4 text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl relative h-full transition-colors hover:border-brand/50 hover:bg-muted/50\"><div data-slot=\"card-header\" class=\"group/card-header @container/card-header grid auto-rows-min items-start gap-1 rounded-t-xl px-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] has-data-[slot=card-description]:grid-rows-[auto_auto] [.border-b]:pb-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:[.border-b]:pb-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-image size-4 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"m21 15-3.086-3.086a2 2 0 0 0-2.828 0L6 21\"></path></svg><div data-slot=\"card-title\" class=\"font-heading font-medium group-data-[size=sm]/card:text-sm text-base\">Image Converter</div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-description\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Bulk convert images between PNG, JPG, WebP, and AVIF with quality controls.</div></div></div></a><a href=\"/tools/media-toolkit/video-trimmer\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card py-4 text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl relative h-full transition-colors hover:border-brand/50 hover:bg-muted/50\"><div data-slot=\"card-header\" class=\"group/card-header @container/card-header grid auto-rows-min items-start gap-1 rounded-t-xl px-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] has-data-[slot=card-description]:grid-rows-[auto_auto] [.border-b]:pb-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:[.border-b]:pb-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-scissors-line-dashed size-4 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5.42 9.42 8 12\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"8\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"m14 6-8.58 8.58\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"16\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"M10.8 14.8 14 18\"></path><path d=\"M16 12h-2\"></path><path d=\"M22 12h-2\"></path></svg><div data-slot=\"card-title\" class=\"font-heading font-medium group-data-[size=sm]/card:text-sm text-base\">Video Trimmer</div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-description\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Quick-cut video clips without re-encoding the entire file. Fast stream copy mode.</div></div></div></a><a href=\"/tools/media-toolkit/audio-extractor\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card py-4 text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl relative h-full transition-colors hover:border-brand/50 hover:bg-muted/50\"><div data-slot=\"card-header\" class=\"group/card-header @container/card-header grid auto-rows-min items-start gap-1 rounded-t-xl px-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] has-data-[slot=card-description]:grid-rows-[auto_auto] [.border-b]:pb-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:[.border-b]:pb-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-music size-4 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 18V5l12-2v13\"></path><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"16\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><div data-slot=\"card-title\" class=\"font-heading font-medium group-data-[size=sm]/card:text-sm text-base\">Audio Extractor</div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-description\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Extract audio tracks from video files. Convert to MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC.</div></div></div></a><a href=\"/tools/media-toolkit/subtitle-extractor\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card py-4 text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl relative h-full transition-colors hover:border-brand/50 hover:bg-muted/50\"><div data-slot=\"card-header\" class=\"group/card-header @container/card-header grid auto-rows-min items-start gap-1 rounded-t-xl px-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] has-data-[slot=card-description]:grid-rows-[auto_auto] [.border-b]:pb-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:[.border-b]:pb-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-captions size-4 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"14\" x=\"3\" y=\"5\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 15h4M15 15h2M7 11h2M13 11h4\"></path></svg><div data-slot=\"card-title\" class=\"font-heading font-medium group-data-[size=sm]/card:text-sm text-base\">Subtitle Extractor</div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-description\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Pull embedded subtitle tracks from MKV, MP4, and other video containers.</div></div></div></a><a href=\"/tools/media-toolkit/metadata-editor\"><div data-slot=\"card\" data-size=\"default\" class=\"group/card flex flex-col gap-4 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card py-4 text-sm text-card-foreground ring-1 ring-foreground/10 has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 has-[&gt;img:first-child]:pt-0 data-[size=sm]:gap-3 data-[size=sm]:py-3 data-[size=sm]:has-data-[slot=card-footer]:pb-0 *:[img:first-child]:rounded-t-xl *:[img:last-child]:rounded-b-xl relative h-full transition-colors hover:border-brand/50 hover:bg-muted/50\"><div data-slot=\"card-header\" class=\"group/card-header @container/card-header grid auto-rows-min items-start gap-1 rounded-t-xl px-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:px-3 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] has-data-[slot=card-description]:grid-rows-[auto_auto] [.border-b]:pb-4 group-data-[size=sm]/card:[.border-b]:pb-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-tags size-4 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M13.172 2a2 2 0 0 1 1.414.586l6.71 6.71a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 0 3.408l-4.592 4.592a2.4 2.4 0 0 1-3.408 0l-6.71-6.71A2 2 0 0 1 6 9.172V3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1z\"></path><path d=\"M2 7v6.172a2 2 0 0 0 .586 1.414l6.71 6.71a2.4 2.4 0 0 0 3.191.193\"></path><circle cx=\"10.5\" cy=\"6.5\" r=\".5\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></svg><div data-slot=\"card-title\" class=\"font-heading font-medium group-data-[size=sm]/card:text-sm text-base\">Metadata Editor</div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-description\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">View, edit, and strip metadata tags from audio and video files.</div></div></div></a></div><div class=\"my-8 flex justify-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"mid-content\"></div></div><section class=\"prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert max-w-none\"><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><div class=\"not-prose mb-10\"></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">What Is the Free Media Toolkit?</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\">The Free Media Toolkit is a growing collection of browser-based tools for working with audio and video files. Every tool runs entirely in your browser using WebAssembly (ffmpeg.wasm) — your files never leave your device, there&#x27;s nothing to install, and no account is required.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\">Whether you need to merge hundreds of audiobook chapters into a single M4A, convert between audio formats, compress a video before sharing, or trim a clip, the Media Toolkit has a dedicated sub-tool for the job. Each tool is individually optimized for its task, so you get a focused, fast experience instead of a bloated all-in-one editor.</p><h2 class=\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Available Tools</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\"><li><strong>Audio Merger</strong> — Combine MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC files into a single output file with optional chapter markers. Ideal for audiobooks and podcast compilations.</li><li><strong>Audio Converter</strong> (coming soon) — Convert between audio formats with configurable quality. Single file or batch mode.</li><li><strong>Video Compressor</strong> (coming soon) — Reduce video file size with quality presets while maintaining visual clarity.</li><li><strong>Video Converter</strong> (coming soon) — Convert between MP4, WebM, MOV, AVI, and GIF formats.</li><li><strong>Audio Trimmer</strong> (coming soon) — Trim audio files or split them at precise time markers.</li><li><strong>Image Converter</strong> (coming soon) — Bulk convert images between PNG, JPG, WebP, and AVIF.</li></ul><h2 class=\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Why Use Browser-Based Media Tools?</h2><div class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\"><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><strong>Privacy</strong> — Your files stay on your device. No uploads, no cloud processing, no data retention policies to worry about.</li><li><strong>No installation</strong>— Works on any modern browser including Chromebooks and locked-down work machines where you can&#x27;t install software.</li><li><strong>No sign-up</strong> — Most online media tools require an account or limit free usage. Every tool here is completely free with no restrictions.</li><li><strong>No file size limits</strong>— The only limit is your browser&#x27;s available memory (typically 1-2 GB on desktop).</li></ul></div><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-tips\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-tips\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Tips from Building <!-- -->the Media Toolkit</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\">Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Pick the tool by the job, not the file type</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Many file types overlap several tools. A video can be converted, compressed, trimmed, or have its audio extracted — pick by what you&#x27;re trying to accomplish, not by the file extension you happen to have.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Run heavy jobs on a desktop, not a phone</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">ffmpeg.wasm runs the same code in any browser, but it scales with available CPU and memory. A 4K video compression that takes 90 seconds on a desktop can take 10+ minutes on a phone — or fail entirely.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Chain tools when one pass isn&#x27;t enough</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Extract audio with one tool, then trim it with another. Convert video, then compress the result. Each tool does one thing well; chain them for compound workflows.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Files never leave your browser tab</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Every tool in the kit processes locally via ffmpeg.wasm. Closing the tab discards the work; refreshing reloads the runtime. Export what you need before navigating away.</p></div></li></ul></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-mistakes\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-mistakes\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Using the converter when the trimmer is what you need</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Re-encoding to change a few seconds of a video is wasteful. If you only need to cut, use the trimmer — it can often stream-copy without re-encoding.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Loading multi-gigabyte files on a low-memory machine</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">ffmpeg.wasm holds decoded streams in memory. For very large files, work in smaller pieces or use the tool on a machine with more RAM.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Expecting cloud-grade speed from in-browser processing</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Cloud-based converters offload work to powerful servers. The toolkit runs on your CPU. The trade-off is privacy and zero upload — at the cost of slower processing for the heaviest jobs.</p></div></li></ul></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-takeaways\" class=\"rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-5\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-takeaways\" class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight\">Key Takeaways</h2><ul class=\"mt-3 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">The Media Toolkit is a browser-based suite for audio, video, and image work — ten tools in one collection.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">Every tool runs locally via ffmpeg.wasm; no upload, no sign-up, no file-size cap beyond your machine&#x27;s memory.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">Chain tools together (extract → trim → convert) for compound workflows without leaving the browser.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">It is a free alternative to Adobe Media Encoder, HandBrake Online, and CloudConvert.</span></li></ul></section><h2 class=\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-4 text-muted-foreground\"><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">How does this work without uploading my files?</h3><p class=\"mt-1\">The Media Toolkit uses ffmpeg.wasm — a WebAssembly port of the industry-standard ffmpeg library. It runs entirely in your browser tab. Your files are read from disk into browser memory, processed by the WASM engine, and the output is downloaded directly to your device.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Is there a file size limit?</h3><p class=\"mt-1\">There&#x27;s no artificial limit. The practical limit is your browser&#x27;s available memory — typically 1-2 GB for the combined size of all input files. A warning appears if your files exceed 1 GB total.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Which browsers are supported?</h3><p class=\"mt-1\">Any modern Chromium-based browser (Chrome, Edge, Brave, Opera) and Firefox. Safari has limited WebAssembly support and may not work with all tools. Desktop browsers are recommended for the best performance.</p></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><aside class=\"hidden w-[300px] shrink-0 lg:block\"><div class=\"sticky top-20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:300px;height:250px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"sidebar\"></div><div id=\"tool-guide-portal\"></div></div></aside></div></div></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Free Tool Shed. All rights reserved.</p><nav class=\"flex gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></nav></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0eyplc079uusk.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\